title: Open Bar #38 - Picard Soars, Ant Man 3 Stumbles, Velma Gets Season 2
description:
Drinker's Log, stardate something something point two, we're en-route to Open Bar with surprising news - Picard Season 3 is really good! Who would have thought we'd be praising a Star Trek show in 2023? Join me, Dave Cullen, Robert Meyer Burnett and MauLer as we talk all things Star Trek.
